headline: 1 Wall Street Analyst Says There's a Great Investment Hiding in Plain Sight. These 2 Dividend Stocks Are My Best Ideas for Investing in It.
summary: The market is in a state of flux thanks to geopolitical issues around tariffs.  One Wall Street pro has a different tactic.  Maura Pape, a senior investment strategist at Bernstein Private Wealth Management, recently highlighted commercial real estate as a good investment opportunity to Bloomberg.
